<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Letter</div>
<div class="nbunit" id="22Nov1918"><font color="red">22 November 1918</font>, <cite>Letters II</cite> (Ezra Pound to JJ): Bloom is a great man, and you have almightily answered the critics &hellip; Has &lsquo;Ulysses&rsquo; 24 Odyssean books? I dont want to ask silly questions, and I hope it continues forever, but people are continuously asking ME about it &hellip; If there are going to be chapters after April, I will try to bone a few quid more out of someone</div>
